			<abstract>
				<p>Testimony of Rachel Amornik regarding her experiences during the final “Aktion” in the Miedzyerzec Podlaski Ghetto, forced labor in
					Majdanek, Skarzysko-Kamienna, and the HASAG camp in Leipzig, and a death march.</p>
			</abstract>

